data.productName: PNY XLR8 Gaming 8GB DDR4 3200MHz SODIMM Laptop RAM
data.description: The PNY XLR8 Gaming 8GB DDR4 3200MHz Laptop RAM is an extreme performance DDR4 Memory designed for laptop gamers and performance enthusiasts. It offers quicker response times and better visuals for a better gaming experience. The XLR8 comes with XMP 2.0 Support. It provides easy overclocking to run at top speed for maximal performance. It delivers 3200MHz performance, and backward compatible with lower frequencies: 3000MHz, 2933MHz, 2666MHz, 2400MHz, 2133MHz. It has a CAS Latency of CL20 and an operating voltage of 1.2V. The PNY XLR8 Gaming Laptop RAM comes with a Lifetime Limited Warranty.
